_count": 103}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "婚姻中，为什么很爱你的人也会出轨?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "走进了婚姻，按理说，两个人都应该保持忠诚。 之后的日子里，都只是看着眼前这个人，和别的异性都保持距离。 然而，不少的婚姻，往往却总是出现了第三个人。 有的是因为感情不好，所以出轨，而还有的人，明明感情挺不错，对另一半也挺好的，看起来挺爱自己的伴侣的，也依旧还是出轨了。 很爱，却还是出轨了，这总是更让人难以相信，同时也难以接受。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-aa46bdbf32598322350d62dff128c4b9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "65 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1065003606"}}, "attached_info": "CkEIneXe7Z7MgZlrEAMaCTExMTE4OTc2OCDSib64BjAAOJ0BQAVyCjEwNjUwMDM2MDZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1730132914.482931", "card_id": "Q_667339584", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 210}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价电影《变形金刚：起源》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "2007 年的《变形金刚》开了个好头，但之后就一路狗尾续貂、越拍越烂。 而今系列重启，又开了个不错的头，希望续作会越拍越好。很明显新故事并非来自于 G1 动画；而是来自于由 G1 衍生发展而来的变形金刚漫画。和 G1 动画比，漫画要宏大、深邃的多。要是以此为基础，新系列拍个十来集都不成问题。 另外，从影片中人物名称的翻译看，明显用了「变形金刚中国联盟」那个版本的翻译。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/667339584"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIneXe7Z7MgZlrEAMaCTExMDU3NTQ4MSCJv6C3BjAAOMsCQAZyCTY2NzMzOTU4NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1730132914.483376", "card_id": "Q_664740545", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e